    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h2>Your Trusted Pharmacy</h2>
      <p>Discover a wide range of safe, effective medicines delivered to your door. Easy browsing, secure checkout, and professional support â€” all in one place.</p>
      <a class="cta" href="/signup">Sign Up and Shop Now</a>
    </div>
    <img src="/uploads/closeup-view-pharmacist-hand-taking-medicine-box-from-shelf-drug-store.jpg" alt="Pharmacy illustration">
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 PharmaPlus. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
